name: Not Your Average Vegetable
description:
Not Your Average Vegetable (VR ONLY)

"You my friend are not special, you are generic. you see others the same way they see you.

This story is not about you. This story takes place at the end of a Knights Time Line, this is what happens after the 'Game Over' screen.

He has been caught. and charged with the failure to complete his farming quest...His punishment?  Make him eat his veggies..."

Created in 15 Hours for KSU Game Jam 2017.

Team No Sleep: Ben Snowden/Noah Schultz


DISCLAIMER: This game is no longer downloadable due to restrictions set by the supervisor of this project. If you have any questions or comments about this game, please post your question in the comments below.
